---
title: Beef Rump & Grilled Veggie Salad  with Homemade Chimichurri Sauce & Charred Lemon
description: This meal is the perfect excuse to take simple ingredients like beef rump and veggies on a spectacular charred flavour journey when they hit the grill. A zingy homemade chimichurri and zesty chargrilled lemon elevate this meal even more. If you don’t have a BBQ, follow along with our stovetop method to enjoy this dinner delight.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
